### ===========================================
### Create Appraisal
### ===========================================
### Creates a new appraisal for a request
### Prerequisites: A request must exist first
POST {{baseUrl}}/appraisals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "requestId": "991495AE-F065-4B2C-8249-B6BEF197CA13",
  "appraisalType": "Full",
  "priority": "High",
  "slaDays": 7
}

